lead_paragraph: Tom Watson bettered his age Friday in the Mitsubishi Electric Championship, leaving him two strokes behind leader Duffy Waldorf in the PGA Tour Champions' opener.

headline.print_headline: Watson Betters Age, Waldorf Leads Champions Tour Opener
